customer-support-bot/
│
├── app.py                   # Flask API to serve the chatbot
├── bot/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── intent_classifier.py # ML-based intent recognition
│   ├── rule_engine.py       # Rule-based response engine
│   └── responses.py         # Predefined bot responses
│
├── data/
│   └── intents.json         # Intent examples and training data
│
├── train.py                 # Script to train the intent classifier
